# Canonical author identities.
#
# Collapses leftover local placeholder identities (eval/t/ferry — set by a
# benchmark/eval harness that left git user.email at <name>@localhost) onto the
# real author. This is display-only: git shortlog/blame/log and the contributor
# graph read it; commit history is not rewritten.
